org.aoplib4j.uml
Class SequenceDiagram

java.lang.Object
  org.aoplib4j.uml.SequenceDiagram

public final class SequenceDiagram
extends java.lang.Object

Class representing a sequence diagram. An instance of this object is created by the AopLib4j framework for every annotated method. A sequence diagram contains a writer used to write the diagram, the maximum depth of the diagram, A sequence diagram is a tree having as nodes instances of SequenceMethod class.

Author:
Adrian Citu
See Also:
SequenceDiagramWriter.write(SequenceMethod), SequenceMethod
